PurpleHawk made the game with a friendly AI that is comedic and fun to play with. Whenever I am looking for a puzzle, this is my go-to. I never found out how to win, though, until I watched a documentary and it mentioned a game like it. Overall, this is 100% four-star game.

TheDancingDuck has made a wonderful project where you insert a coin into a really cool looking shape art prize machine. Then you turn the handle and wait a few seconds and you can get a random emoji! Great for when you have nothing else to do
